{"tid":613764,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚去飲，兩邊人爭啲大打出手","createTime":"2018-04-02T03:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T04:00:56.000Z","uid":5077,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85759d0fd099aab87632dcdbe773b02fe25ac321","tid":613764,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"尋晚表哥結婚擺酒，請咗好多親戚朋友去，<br />\n去到見到咁熱鬧，我都好開心，<br />\n事關細個嗰陣同我玩得最埋嘅就係表哥，<br />\n但到咗咁耐都未見過新娘出嚟，<br />\n由頭到尾都係表哥同佢個兄弟喺到行嚟行去，<br />\n啲親戚就開始起哄，<br />\n話想見吓表哥娶咩老婆要收到咁密實，<br />\n點知表哥話原來個兄弟就係佢另一半...<br />\n之後老一輩嘅親戚接受唔到，開始癡癡地線，<br />\n又係咁灌酒，又手舞足蹈，又跳嚟跳去，<br />\n有幾個呀伯仲攬埋一齊打茄輪添。<br />\n<br />\n嚟到呢到，我開始發現表哥嘅奸計，<br />\n表哥從來都係一個好重心計嘅gay佬，<br />\n以前佢曾經為咗一睹我七尺巨龍嘅風采，<br />\n竟然呃晒我成家上佢屋企食飯，<br />\n仲將全屋水換晒做迷姦水，<br />\n一諗起呢到，我大概知表哥喺到玩緊咩詭計啦。"},{"pid":"c0f1f72cc0208d071e8f0e93a6bb8a86813ad108","tid":613764,"uid":139974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2feeab1c8138037e6ac5c6f43990dcd41d16ecce","tid":613764,"uid":60838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"警方列作傻人發現案處理"},{"pid":"87867e6f6de3255d7068b48b6c78810b3f1532f8","tid":613764,"uid":51041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母睇完成篇野都唔撚知你up乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"aad5fb81d293009bf6c93efecd41cd0c233c725a","tid":613764,"uid":137766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"Gay佬就Gay佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a541d75c2f71bb5c3ca510f28f705184be8a6f","tid":613764,"uid":32721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:39:10.000Z","msg":"樓主玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩到痴鳩左線"},{"pid":"93f2215ad702407ac715d6267ae2acdf6ed0a47a","tid":613764,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:00:56.000Z","msg":"新會然"}]}